            "subtype": "ability",
            "success": "As failure, but the creature takes half damage and is not confused.",
            "text": "The mocking chorus adopts the voices of its enemies, spreading lies and jeers among would-be allies and tearing apart trusted friends. Creatures in a 60-foot emanation of the mocking chorus must attempt a DC 37 Will save. The mocking chorus can't use petty whispers again for 1 minute.",
